{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "第十三回\"醋海风波\"讲述了陆小凤在船上经历的一场惊心动魄的对峙。故事从老实和尚突然出现并送来一碗牛肉汤开始，陆小凤发现这是\"牛肉汤\"所做。小玉随后现身，透露是她暗中策划了沙曼的逃脱，并吊起又放下了老实和尚。当老实和尚喝下牛肉汤后中毒倒地，众人意识到汤里被下了药。此时牛肉汤本人现身，她精心打扮后与众人对峙。沙曼和小玉联手制服牛肉汤，逼迫她脱光衣服。牛肉汤趁机挟持陆小凤为人质，反过来威胁沙曼和小玉。关键时刻陆小凤出手反击，将牛肉汤摔倒在地。最终陆小凤制定了用牛肉汤作为筹码去与宫九谈判的计划，准备用她换取逃生机会，沙曼虽然担忧但只能放手让他去冒险。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰，砰，砰，请开门。你是谁？我是老公鸡。你来干什么？来送牛肉汤，小鸡们喝了长得壮，不怕风来不怕浪。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "和尚老实，菩萨保佑和尚！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "菩萨杀不杀牛？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我佛戒杀生，菩萨怎么会杀牛？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "菩萨也不会给和尚喝牛肉汤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "当然不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "那么这碗牛肉汤是从哪里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你猜呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这碗牛肉汤是你的一位老朋友叫和尚送给你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "哦！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "她说你们两位这两天一定劳动过度，一定很需要滋补滋补。这些话可不是和尚说的，和尚本来也不想说，可是你那位朋友却一定要和尚转告给你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "她的人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "她说她很快就会来看你，叫你别着急。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "我也有几句话要请你转告给她。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "和尚洗耳恭听。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "你就说我宁可去陪母狗吃屎，也不愿再见她，再喝她的牛肉汤。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好好的一个人，为什么偏偏要去陪母狗吃屎呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "小玉！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你能不能不要去陪母狗？能不能去陪公狗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "因为我要陪你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你为什么一定不让他去陪母狗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "因为我怕曼姑娘吃醋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们吃醋，我吃牛肉汤。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来这世上并不止牛肉汤一个人会做这种牛肉汤。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "还有谁会？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我只会吃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "这不是你做的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我不但会吃，还会偷，这是我从厨房里偷来的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "厨房里有人会做这种牛肉汤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只有一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "牛肉汤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "其实你应该想得到，这次她当然也上了船。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "为什么她当然要来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我偷偷的藏起了一条小船，所以她就认为你们一定是坐船跑了，否则他们怎么会找不到？就因为找不到你们，这两天九少爷和宫主的脾气都大得要命，幸好他们做梦也想不到这些事是谁做的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "究竟是谁做的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "是你？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "除了我还有谁？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "是你把沙曼送来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "当然是我。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "把这和尚吊起来的也是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "把他放下来的也是我。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你不信我能做得出这种事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "连你都不信，九少爷和宫主当然更不信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "所以他们想不到是你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "连做梦都想不到。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这有什么好笑，和尚也是人，肚子饿了也会叫。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "可是和尚的肚子好像叫得特别好听。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "可惜和尚自己一点都不喜欢听。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "和尚喜欢什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "和尚只喜欢看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "看什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "看馒头、看咸菜、看萝卜干，只要能吃的，和尚都喜欢看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "牛肉汤不好看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "和尚不吃荤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "那么和尚只有饿着，听和尚自己的肚子叫。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "曼姑娘也不吃牛肉汤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "不吃。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "曼姑娘不饿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "不饿，就算饿也不吃。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "原来曼姑娘真的是在吃醋，原来吃醋也能吃得饱的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她不吃我吃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "和尚几时开始吃荤的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "饿疯了的时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "酒肉穿肠过，佛在心头坐，和尚吃点牛肉汤，其实也没太大关系。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "的确没关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有关系。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "大得要命的关系，和尚……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这碗汤里下了药。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁下的药？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我正想问你。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这件事不是我做的，不是我……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "不是你是谁？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是她是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我知道你一定不会对我怎么样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你特地打扮好来给我看，当然不会对我怎么样。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我当然不会对你怎么样，我只不过想要你去陪母狗吃屎罢了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你想干什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我也不想干什么，只不过想要你陪和尚喝汤！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "这碗汤炖得好，不喝光了实在可惜。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你敢？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我为什么不敢？我看得出你已经在害怕了，因为你本来以为我们会怕你，可是我们不怕，所以你就害怕了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "想不到曼姑娘的剑法这么好。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "这世上想不到的事本来就很多。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "牛肉汤里加上和尚的口水，不知是不是好吃一点？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "其实你应该高兴才对，不管怎么样，和尚的口水总是很难吃得到的嘛。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我很高兴，高兴得要命。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你高兴就好，我就是怕你不高兴。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你们是不是可以让我走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "不可以。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "你还想要我干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "脱光。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "脱光？把什么脱光？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "把全身上下都脱光，能脱的都脱光。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你用不着看着他，他又不是没有看过你脱光。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她脱得真快。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "因为她经常都在脱。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只奇怪她为什么总是不会着凉。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好棒的身材，我若是男子，现在一定已晕了过去。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "只可惜你不是男人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "幸好我不是，你也不是嘛！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们也不是女人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你们想要做一个真正的女人，还得多学学。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你可以教我们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你为什么不脱光，让我教给你？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你再动一动，他就死。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "小玉，小宝贝，我喜欢你，一直都很喜欢你，你记不记得小的时候我就常常抱着你睡觉？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "现在你如果替我杀了沙曼，我一定更喜欢你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是不是真的想他死？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我能不能要你们做件事？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "脱光，两个女子统统脱光，能脱的都脱光。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我数到十，你们如果还没有脱光，这里就多了个死人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你们也是经常脱惯了衣服的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你为什么等到现在才出手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我本来想等她数到十才出手的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是不是想强奸我？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我倒没兴趣，他也没有这必要。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你们就该赶快让我走，否则你们也跑不了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要有片刻看不见我，九哥就会到处找我的，在这条船上，你们能往哪里跑？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "小玉，小宝贝，快把你的腿拿开，你抵得我好痒。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这船上有没有救生用的小艇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "有两条。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "有没有人保护？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "守护的人，我们可以对付，可是我们就算抢到也没有用。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "现在上面的人还不知道小玉的反叛，她若去夺小艇，想必不难。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "现在这时候，宫九通常在什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "在他的舱房里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "除了他之外，这船上还有没有别的高手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他一向独来独往。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "他的舱房，当然就是这条船的主舱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你……你是不是想去找他？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "本来也不想去的，可是现在却不能不去了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "因为你有样东西非卖给他不可，他好像也非买不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "什么东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "一大碗又香又浓的牛肉汤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你想要什么价钱？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "我要的价钱并不高。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "也许宫九并不想要这碗牛肉汤，也许他只想要你的命。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "无论做什么事，多少总得冒点风险的！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们只要看到宫九一个人走上甲板，没有看见我……",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那么我们立刻就杀了她？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你……准备什么时候走？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "和尚一醒我就走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "当然要等他醒，箱子总得有个男人来扛的！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在和尚还没有醒来，箱子还空着，难道你们就让它空着？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    }
